'''Grimpen''' was a corrupt [[B'omarr Order/Legends|B'omarr monk]] who worked for [[Jabba Desilijic Tiure/Legends|Jabba Desilijic Tiure]]. He lured [[Tash Arranda/Legends|Tash Arranda]] into a trap, but his plans were foiled by her [[Zak Arranda/Legends|brother]]. The rest of the B'omarr Order punished him, by removing his [[Brain/Legends|brain]], so that he would never be able to feel enlightenment.

